  "instructions": [
    "heat 1 tsp of sesame oil in a large saucepan over medium-high heat.",
    "add 2 cloves of minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add 1-inch piece of grated ginger and cook for 30 seconds, until fragrant.",
    "add 8 oz of rigatoni and cook for 2 minutes, until lightly toasted.",
    "add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "reduce heat to medium-low and simmer for 10-12 minutes, or until the rigatoni is al dente.",
    "remove from heat and stir in 2 tbsp of gochujang, 1 tsp of fish sauce, and 1 tsp of soy sauce.",
    "whisk until smooth, then season with salt to taste.",
    "transfer to a serving bowl and top with 1/4 cup of chopped green onions, 2 tbsp of toasted sesame seeds, and 1/4 cup of chopped scallions.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
